title: My other account doesnt have the Icon or Riot Kayle skin yet.
body: I played a game on it the day of the announcement and on the 19th, both were Co-Op vs AI. The day of the announcement was when i got my other account to level 5. Its IGN is Warporo.

replies.body: We're not done sending out gifts to everyone, and we'll be getting to more recently eligible players as well!  Stay up to date through our current [support banner](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/227317608--Sept-14-Anniversary-gifts-are-currently-being-distributed-You-may-not-receive-them-right-away-so-please-be-patient-).  Patience!
